label: DS100
description: Double Switch in a dual relay in-wall module.
info_overview: Vemmio Double Switch is a dual relay in-wall module. The product works as a transceiver and is a Z-Wave Plus enabled device. Mini size design lets the module be easily hidden into the wall box to do not interfere with house decoration. One of many uses of the Double Switch is to turn on or off the connected fittings and monitor power consumption in real time. The new smart relay calibration technology can work perfectly with many kinds of lights like: incandescent, fluorescent and LED lights.
info_inclusion: Pressing Z-Wave button three times within 2 seconds will enter inclusion mode.
info_exclusion: Pressing Z-Wave button three times within 2 seconds will enter exclusion mode.
category_description: Any device attached to the wall that controls a binary status of something, for ex. a light switch

associations.label: Group 2
associations.overview:
For group 2, the Switch will report

  1. ON/OFF status of Relay1 
  2. Instant Power Consumption (Watt) of Relay1
  3. Accumulated Power Consumption (KWh) of Relay1 to Z-Wave Controller.

associations.label: Group 3
associations.overview:
For group 3, the Switch will report

  1. ON/OFF status of Relay2
  2. Instant Power Consumption (Watt) of Relay2
  3. Accumulated Power Consumption (KWh) of Relay2 to Z-Wave Controller.
